Pointer to pass to push callback. See \fICURLMOPT_PUSHDATA(3)\fP
.IP CURLMOPT_PUSHFUNCTION
Callback that approves or denies server pushes. See \fICURLMOPT_PUSHFUNCTION(3)\fP
